Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs25\fax0.1\c&H9C84EB&\fsp3\bord0\b0\frz29.19\pos(714.667,424.934)}绝密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要照着做就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这副眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟神宫寺见过你  得乔装一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,被冰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,本神居然被冰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  店开着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,选一个喜欢的位置坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,重新一看还真是个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,首先你要作为客人进入店里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吃一碗她们的招牌面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就从这里开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一碗招牌拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  天升拉面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是中午却没有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家主打无添加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  味道还不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,味道不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但却没有让人有想再吃一次的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要获取她的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我是做这个的
